==Sinopsis
ReadableNumbers converts a given number to its letter version.


==Repository
    git://github.com/edgarjs/readable-numbers.git

==Home
    http://mimbles.net

==Usage
*Integers*
    1738.to_letter will produce:
	mil setecientos treinta y ocho
    421.to_currency will produce:
	cuatrocientos veintiun pesos M.N.

*Floats*
    314.12.to_letter will produce:
	trescientos catorce punto doce
    94.50.to_currency will produce:
	noventa y cuatro pesos con cincuenta centavos M.N.

*Negatives*
    -31.to_letter will produce:
	menos treinta y uno
    -2.14.to_letter will produce:
	menos dos punto catorce

<b>Octals, binaries, and others</b>
    010.to_letter (octal 010 = decimal 8) will produce:
	ocho
    0b10.to_letter (binary 10 = decimal 2) will produce:
	dos
    0x1A.to_letter (hex 1AC = decimal 26) will produce:
	veintiseis


==Notes
Currently the plugin supports only Spanish language, but it's intended to be
automatically localizable through GetText (probably).


